						<summary>

						<p>On a slab in a field to the east of the village.</p>						

						<p>Rāmadēva II. Ś. 1547: 1625 A.D.</p>						

						<p>The details of the date, <hi rend="italic">viz.</hi>, Śaka 1547, Krōdhana, Vṛiśchika, śu. 7 are insufficient for verification.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land by one Veṅkaṭṭappa-nāyakkar, grandson of Tāmal Veṅkaṭappa-nāyakkar, and son of <hi rend="italic">Rāyasa</hi> Cheṉṉappa, to Pērambala-Paṇḍāram and others for their services to god Chē(Kshē)ttira-īśvarar of Tirukkaḻukkuṉṟam.</p>						

						</summary>
